### =====================================================
### SCENARIO 1: Valid expense under $100 → Auto-approved
### =====================================================
POST https://func-cst8917-rohan-va.azurewebsites.net/api/expenses/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_name": "Rohan Surti",
  "employee_email": "rohan@example.com",
  "amount": 50,
  "category": "meals",
  "description": "Team lunch during project meeting",
  "manager_email": "manager@example.com"
}

### After sending:
### Copy "statusQueryGetUri" and open it to see result


